---
title: Sesame Beef and Broccoli Noodles with Carrots and Green Onions
description: The next time you're craving a big bowl of noodles, we've got you covered! Nutty sesame oil makes this beef and broccoli noodle dish wonderfully aromatic, while hoisin sauce, soy sauce and garlic build deep flavour. Tonight, spaghetti takes the place of noodles; a swap you never knew you'd love.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nouilles-au-brocoli-et-au-boeuf-au-sesame-b78568ac.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/sesame-beef-and-broccoli-noodles-638ee1961b9f98fb82021799-b6f17787.pdf
